= Code Sprint - Boston  - 2018 =

== Dates ==

 * Start at 09:00 Wednesday September 26
 * End at 17:00 Friday September 28

== Sponsors ==

Sponsorship dollars will be used to support travel and accommodation for "non-corporate" developers whose travel is not otherwise covered. Interested in sponsoring? Please contact <lr at pcorp dot us>.

We are able to accept payments in the form of Credit Card, Bank Transfer, Pay Pal, and for US companies (all the already stated plus checks)

