== Goals ==

The main aim is to begin thinking about next releases, and major features to be attempted.

 * wiki:PostGIS3 topics
 * PostGIS 2.5 ticket triage (if not released yet) otherwise work/planning for  PostGIS 3.0
 * PostgreSQL integration
  * Desired core improvements
  * Core features we should make use of
 * Discuss feasibility / strategies for geography clustering implementations
 * Performance testing suite
 * web site refresh, infra wars
 * What goes in NEWS file and announcments
 * Add your own ... ?

